Name:             %PACKAGE_NAME%
Summary:          Client library for GoodData REST-ful API
Version:          %VERSION%
Release:          %RELEASE%
Vendor:           GoodData
Group:            Applications/Productivity

License:          GoodData
URL:              https://github.com:gooddata/www-gooddata.git
Source0:          %{name}-%{version}.tar
BuildRoot:        %{_tmppath}/%{name}-%{version}-root
Requires:         perl
BuildRequires:    perl perl-Module-Build

%description
WWW::GoodData is the client for GoodData JSON-based API built atop
WWW::GoodData::Agent client agent, with focus on usefullness and
correctness of implementation.

It provides code for navigating the REST-ful API structure as well as
wrapper funcitons for common actions.

%prep
%setup -q -c

%build
perl ./Build.PL

%install
./Build install destdir=$RPM_BUILD_ROOT/
find "$RPM_BUILD_ROOT" -type f -o -type l |
    sed "s|^${RPM_BUILD_ROOT}||" > mainpkg.files

%clean
rm -rf $RPM_BUILD_ROOT
rm -Rf mainpkg.files

%files -f mainpkg.files
